===================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES
   bedtools
   tabix
   VAT (variant annotation tool)
   TFM-pvalue
   bigWigAverageOverBed
   Perl package Parallele::ForkManager

